item.title: Shiloh
item.description:
Shiloh

“Now Shiloh I don’t want you to be nervous, but we’re going to do a little experiment; your father told me your favorite subject at school is science, and that you’re the best at experiments”, said Dr. Sabini as she placed a folded bandana over Shiloh’s eyes.
